<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> That last one happened right here on FV at the skeleton ruins epic monk camp that TLCs at level 10. Damn TLC turning a dumb level 6 skeleton into a KS'ing free-for-all. Guide came, told them to leave me alone, watched them swear and cuss and yell at me, KS me more, train me, etc. etc.. Guide kept telling them to stop and they ignored her. Nothing ever happened to them. Players have to recognize the guide as an authority in order for a guide to be effective. GMs don't need any such approval from players.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
