Then that Guide didn't do what they could have.  Every time they curse they could have gotten a warning.  Every time they killed an engaged mob, they could have gotten a warning.  These are official, and are added to your account.  When your account has 4, a GM comes in a bans you.  So the Guide isn't allowed to summon you, and bind you in the jail, but they can fill out the paperwork to get a GM to.<br>
